Privacy policy for the application of a pipe-lamp

How information is collected

You must provide us with personal information such as your name, contact number and email.

Personal information you provide
If you want to use the application, you must create an account. To create your account, the application will request personally identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify you, which may include your name, phone number, and email address. It will be up to you to decide how much information you want to share as part of your profile. You can review and review your profile at any time.

This data is used only temporarily in order to provide a better service for you, and your data is not shared with any third party.

Information about your geographical location is collected in order to display services near you.
